comments: Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Hield's (SAC) path and absorbs the contact on the pick.
Holmes (SAC) has a resting forearm on Conley's (UTA) side and he does not extend or deliver any contact with it during the driving shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Conley's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact on the pick.
O'Neale (UTA) and Barnes (SAC) come together and incidental body contact occurs during the rebound.
Holmes (SAC) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Gobert's (UTA) arm, which does not affect his ability to secure the rebound and maintain control of the ball.
Holmes (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Mitchell (UTA).
Fox (SAC) makes contact with Gobert's (UTA) arm, which affects his shot near the rim.
Gobert (UTA) is drawn into the air and makes contact with Fox's (SAC) body which affects his shot near the rim.
Conley (UTA) disengages from Holmes (SAC) on the perimeter and marginal arm contact occurs, which does not affect his ability to defend.
After the pass is cleanly deflected, Conley (UTA) and Mitchell (SAC) both pursue the loose ball and incidental body contact occurs as the reach for the ball.
Mitchell (UTA) makes contact with Fox's (SAC) arm, which affects his shot near the rim.
Haliburton (SAC) jumps straight up and marginal contact occurs to Conley's (UTA) shoulder, which does not affect his ability to make his intended pass.
O'Neale (UTA) steps on the sideline out of bounds as he dribbles the ball up the court.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in Bogdanovic's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs as he slightly extends his arms out on the screen.
Fox (SAC) moves into and makes contact with Mitchell's (UTA) body, which affects his SQBR.
Gobert (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Barnes (SAC).
Hield (SAC) and O'Neale (UTA) engage and disengage while reaching for the rebound.
Hield (SAC) makes contact with Gobert's (UTA) arm, which affects his SQBR.
Gobert (UTA) momentarily places a resting hand on Mitchell's (SAC) shoulder and marginal contact occurs as he removes it, before cleanly blocking the driving shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Gobert (UTA).
